@startuml filter-workflow

title LogViewer - Filter Application Workflow

actor User
participant FilterPanel
participant FilterManager
participant Filter
participant EventsContainer
participant UIModel
participant EventsTableView

User -> FilterPanel: Create/Edit Filter
FilterPanel -> FilterManager: addFilter(filter)
activate FilterManager

FilterManager -> Filter: Compile pattern
activate Filter
Filter -> Filter: Build regex/strategy
deactivate Filter

User -> FilterPanel: Apply Filter
FilterPanel -> FilterManager: applyFilters(criteria)

FilterManager -> FilterManager: For each filter:\nCheck if enabled
FilterManager -> EventsContainer: GetEvent(index)
EventsContainer -> Filter: matches(event)

Filter -> Filter: Evaluate all conditions
note right of Filter
    Multiple conditions
    combined with AND logic
end note
Filter --> FilterManager: bool result

FilterManager -> FilterManager: Accumulate matching\nindices

FilterManager --> UIModel: NotifyDataChanged()\nwith filtered results

UIModel -> EventsTableView: Update filtered view
EventsTableView -> EventsTableView: Refresh display
EventsTableView --> User: Show filtered events

User -> FilterPanel: Disable/Remove Filter
FilterPanel -> FilterManager: applyFilters(criteria)
FilterManager --> UIModel: NotifyDataChanged()
UIModel -> EventsTableView: Refresh
EventsTableView --> User: Show all events again

@enduml
